#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.not_equal.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.not\\_equal"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.not_equal.not_equal:1 of
msgid "Return (x1 != x2) element-wise."
msgstr "返回 (x1 != x2) 的逐元素比较结果。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.not_equal.not_equal of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.not_equal.not_equal:3
#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.not_equal.not_equal:5 of
msgid "Input tensors."
msgstr "输入张量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.not_equal.not_equal:7 of
msgid ""
"A location into which the result is stored. If provided, it must have a "
"shape that the inputs broadcast to. If not provided or `None`, a freshly-"
"allocated tensor is returned. A tuple (possible only as a keyword "
"argument) must have length equal to the number of outputs."
msgstr ""
"用于存储结果的位置。如果提供了该参数，则其形状必须可广播为输入张量的形状"
"。如果未提供或为 `None`，则返回一个新分配的张量。元组（只能作为关键字参数"
"）的长度必须等于输出的数量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.not_equal.not_equal:12 of
msgid ""
"Values of True indicate to calculate the ufunc at that position, values "
"of False indicate to leave the value in the output alone."
msgstr "为 True 的值表示在该位置计算 ufunc，为 False 的值表示保留输出中的原有值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.not_equal.not_equal of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.not_equal.not_equal:17 of
msgid ""
"**not_equal** -- For each element in `x1, x2`, return True if `x1` is not"
" equal to `x2` and False otherwise."
msgstr ""
"**not_equal** -- 对于 `x1, x2` 中的每个元素，如果 `x1` 不等于 `x2` 则返回"
" True，否则返回 False。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.not_equal.not_equal of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.not_equal.not_equal:21 of
msgid ""
":py:obj:`equal`, :py:obj:`greater`, :py:obj:`greater_equal`, "
":py:obj:`less`, :py:obj:`less_equal`"
msgstr ""

